column5: For Engleheart/Timmins/Swastika area for some trout fishing. Checking out some info we have and fishing other spots that weve fished before. Hope to have a nice report next week sometime
Awesome stuff!!! I'm leaving next Tuesday/Wednesday night/morning for Temagami area...good luck!! Hope to see a good report when you're back
Have fun Guys !!! Johnny.. don't think I'm gonna get the airplane up there in time to track you down.. but we'll see. 12' Tinny and canoe??? Musky or Specks... enjoy the trip !!
